  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides basic functionality for describing the structure of a data source at design time.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 Implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema> interface to describe a custom data source at design time. For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema>, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.XmlDocumentSchema>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TypeSchema> classes implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema> interface.  
  
 Classes that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema> are used by custom control designer components to provide lists of fields and views for data-bound controls at design time.  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
