## Remarks  
 A class that implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceSchema.GetViews%2A> method returns an array of objects that implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema> interface. For example, in the array returned by the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetSchema.GetViews%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> method, each element of the array is a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DataSetViewSchema> object that implements <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.IDataSourceViewSchema>.  
  
 ]]></format>
